summary: A retext of Gloria white armor
descriptionHtml:
KURESE Gloria armor from Oblivion ported to skyrim from Dimon99. 
There are two outfits in this mod, black and white. This is my custom retext of white armor.


INSTALL
First install original mod from here http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12595#content
Then install my mod and overwrite files.

_________________________________________________________________________________________

Gredits: to Dimon99 and whoever else was the creator of this armor.
